column5: What a great evening for a stroll along the water tonight.Calm and sunny and warm. For those wondering if the lake is high,well heres yer answer.   Those steps are usually level with the dock in the summer months. A few pics of the marina. Was nice to just sit and soak in some rays,long time coming.      After about a half hour of that we started walking again and low and behold,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,  Number one son is catching a feed for thier dinner.        Then  this little angel appears.    So after a quick visit, we are off to finish our walk.  OH, OH, I know this aint no 4lt jug.LOL
I was wondering where I lost my Muskie float...

Nope, definatly not a 4 ltr jug B.  Must be one of them new fangled drink boxes or something  I did my run tonight too, 6,700 steps on the counter.  Wish I had the view you do tho, and maybe stop for a fish on the way  Joey
it another one of those fancy Irish drinkin glasses...
I guess it would be too much weight to carry a rod and reel with you?... y'all could take turns carrying it yanno!
i wouldnt drink the stuff in it
Did ya return it to the beer store for the deposit?
